# {{TOOLS_DIR}}

Agent tooling for {{PROJECT_NAME}}, generated by agentkit.

- `skills/` — agent skills (`{{SKILL_CORE}}` is the master router).
- `checks/` — config-driven validators (standard-library only). They read
  `agentkit.toml` from the repository root.
- `resync_skills.sh` — re-mirror `{{DOCS_AGENT_DIR}}/*` into skill `references/`.
- `docs_sync_rules.toml` — "change X ⇒ update doc Y" rules for `check_docs_sync.py`.

## Running the checks

    python3 {{TOOLS_DIR}}/check.py --strict                   # run them all
    python3 {{CHECKS_DIR}}/check_tasks.py --root . --strict   # run one

Every check takes `--root` and `--strict` and follows the exit-code convention:
`0` pass / `1` strict failure / `2` usage or environment.
